As a teenager Mort has a temprement making him unsuited to the Family business (Farming). 

Mort's father Lezek takes him to a Job Fair much, I'm sure, like the one at the end of this course.

Mort has no luck attracting the interests of someone to apprectice under. He stays behind out of shame. At midnight, a chap in a cloak, carrying a Sithe turns up... 

Events unfold.
